52
00:03:47,681 --> 00:03:51,890
<i>"But Jesus answered,
'Man shall not live on bread alone…'"</i>

53
00:03:51,973 --> 00:03:53,223
<i>Psst!</i>

54
00:03:53,931 --> 00:03:54,931
<i>Pancho.</i>

55
00:03:55,973 --> 00:03:56,931
<i>Pancho!</i>

56
00:03:57,015 --> 00:03:59,640
<i>…and gave it
to them, saying, "This is my body…"</i>

57
00:03:59,723 --> 00:04:01,931
<i>Pancho, for Numa. Numa.</i>

58
00:04:02,015 --> 00:04:06,848
<i>We proclaim your death,
O Lord, and profess your resurrection</i>

59
00:04:06,931 --> 00:04:09,181
<i>until you come again, Jesus.</i>

60
00:04:09,265 --> 00:04:12,348
<i>Come on, Alfredo.</i>

61
00:04:12,431 --> 00:04:13,973
<i>Hey! You!</i>

62
00:04:14,056 --> 00:04:16,473
<i>Come here. Come here. Come here.</i>

63
00:04:16,556 --> 00:04:18,598
<i>Hand this paper to Pancho. Right there.</i>

64
00:04:22,431 --> 00:04:23,556
<i>Thanks.</i>

65
00:04:23,640 --> 00:04:25,348
<i>Psst, Numa.</i>

66
00:04:26,431 --> 00:04:28,640
<i>Excuse me. Can you hand this to him?</i>

67
00:04:29,848 --> 00:04:30,931
<i>Gastón.</i>

68
00:04:35,390 --> 00:04:39,640
<i>COME TO CHILE, MAN!</i>

69
00:04:39,723 --> 00:04:43,098
<i>Workers and students,
hand in hand, we stand!</i>

70
