73
00:04:51,973 --> 00:04:54,973
<i>-For two weeks. Just look outside!
-It's not about the test.</i>

74
00:04:55,056 --> 00:04:58,265
<i>-I don't care about rugby.
-Rugby? Rugby's the least of it!</i>

75
00:04:58,348 --> 00:05:02,181
<i>Santiago de Chile, $45.
