<i>Daniel Fernández.</i>

1223
02:02:11,390 --> 02:02:12,598
<i>Adolfo Strauch.</i>

1224
02:02:13,598 --> 02:02:15,098
<i>Adolfo Strauch.</i>

1225
02:02:27,431 --> 02:02:29,015
<i>There they are! There they are!</i>

1226
02:02:29,098 --> 02:02:30,681
<i>It's all of them!</i>

1227
02:02:30,765 --> 02:02:32,431
<i>All of them! Hey!</i>

1228
02:03:01,140 --> 02:03:03,056
<i>-Come on! Let's go!
-Whoo!</i>

1229
02:03:03,140 --> 02:03:04,515
<i>Let's go!</i>

1230
02:03:09,806 --> 02:03:11,473
<i>We're going home!</i>

1231
02:03:25,515 --> 02:03:27,931
<i>Come on, Roy! Get up, man!</i>

1232
02:03:33,473 --> 02:03:37,265
<i>-Come on, Gustavo!
-Hey! Leave it! Leave it!</i>

1233
02:03:37,348 --> 02:03:40,056
<i>-What do you mean?
-Put it down!</i>

1234
02:03:41,556 --> 02:03:43,056
<i>Stop! Stop!</i>

1235
02:03:43,140 --> 02:03:45,723
<i>-Gustavo, let's go!
-No! I'm not going without the luggage!</i>

1236
02:03:45,806 --> 02:03:47,931
<i>-No!
-Get in! Get in! What are you doing?</i>

1237
02:03:48,015 --> 02:03:49,848
